304
00:20:07,360 --> 00:20:08,880
I am sorry. Su Tang.

305
00:20:12,560 --> 00:20:13,800
I am sorry.

306
00:20:36,640 --> 00:20:40,360
Master. I entrust Su Tang to you.

307
00:20:43,600 --> 00:20:45,320
