the best way to protect you.

313
00:21:03,760 --> 00:21:05,040
If you leave,

314
00:21:05,760 --> 00:21:08,400
how about your Force of Spirit Lock?

315
00:21:08,520 --> 00:21:09,000
Master.

316
00:21:11,080 --> 00:21:12,200
I don’t want much.

317
00:21:17,320 --> 00:21:18,920
I only want to be a common man.

318
00:21:20,720 --> 00:21:22,120
But the talent of Force of Awakening

319
00:21:22,120 --> 00:21:24,320
didn’t give me this chance to be normal.

320
00:21:24,400 --> 00:21:26,800
It brings only fetter.

321
00:21:28,880 --> 00:21:30,200
My talent.

322
00:21:32,000 --> 00:21:33,880
I’d better control it.

323
00:21:35,320 --> 00:21:36,120
Right?

324
00:21:49,640 --> 00:21:50,760
Have a nice sleep.

325
00:21:53,600 --> 00:21:55,200
Don’t think about anything.

326
00:21:57,440 --> 00:21:58,680
I will take care of

327
