334
00:22:38,480 --> 00:22:40,800
if you are only a maid?

335
00:22:43,320 --> 00:22:44,160
Ling Ziyan.

336
00:22:45,320 --> 00:22:46,480
When did you start to

337
00:22:46,600 --> 00:22:48,040
work for His Majesty?

338
00:22:55,720 --> 00:22:57,720
