346
00:23:20,680 --> 00:23:22,960
I didn’t do it for myself.

347
00:23:26,800 --> 00:23:27,520
Xifan.

348
00:23:29,360 --> 00:23:31,040
You are the only one who treats me

349
00:23:31,040 --> 00:23:33,040
with your whole heart and equality.

350
00:23:33,720 --> 00:23:35,780
His Majesty said if Lu Ping won’t die,

351
00:23:35,840 --> 00:23:37,080
