353
00:23:39,920 --> 00:23:42,400
between you two.

354
00:23:49,520 --> 00:23:51,920
Some things you are not hardhearted enough to do,

355
00:23:51,920 --> 00:23:52,880
or you can’t do.

356
00:23:54,880 --> 00:23:56,080
I will do them for you.

357
00:23:59,240 --> 00:24:00,960
Whatever I did,

358
00:24:01,600 --> 00:24:03,280
I did it for you.

359
00:24:04,200 --> 00:24:05,360
Ling Ziyan.

360
00:24:06,640 --> 00:24:08,320
I will never do anything

361
