377
00:25:11,160 --> 00:25:12,480
You brat.

378
00:25:13,880 --> 00:25:16,480
Now you can stay in Wuyou Valley.

379
00:25:17,760 --> 00:25:19,360
It’s my fault.

380
00:25:20,040 --> 00:25:22,920
