384
00:25:29,760 --> 00:25:30,760
and bother you.

385
00:25:31,480 --> 00:25:34,400
I will leave a safe and peaceful Wuyou Valley to you.

386
00:25:34,960 --> 00:25:35,720
Son.

387
00:25:40,480 --> 00:25:41,610
You’d better leave.

388
00:25:41,920 --> 00:25:43,760
There’s no use standing here for long.

389
00:25:43,760 --> 00:25:45,840
Master won’t meet you.

390
00:25:49,960 --> 00:25:50,960
Mo Chuangu.

391
00:25:51,280 --> 00:25:52,810
No one is allowed in valley.

392
00:25:52,920 --> 00:25:54,280
Get them out.

393
00:25:59,080 --> 00:25:59,680
Master.

394
00:26:00,520 --> 00:26:02,480
The boy rushed into the mist forest recklessly.

395
00:26:02,480 --> 00:26:05,010
