396
00:26:05,680 --> 00:26:07,960
It’s a human.

397
00:26:09,200 --> 00:26:10,600
I am Yan Xifan.

398
00:26:11,080 --> 00:26:12,680
I hope I could meet Master Mo.

399
00:26:43,000 --> 00:26:44,680
How dare you to come?

400
00:26:45,640 --> 00:26:48,440
Wuyou Valley is a place to live a sequestered life.

401
00:26:49,560 --> 00:26:50,960
If you didn’t come,

402
00:26:51,640 --> 00:26:54,320
