407
00:27:06,680 --> 00:27:07,560
I know.

408
00:27:08,680 --> 00:27:10,080
All because of me.

409
00:27:11,360 --> 00:27:12,520
I’m here today

410
00:27:13,400 --> 00:27:15,080
to let you deal with me.

411
00:27:15,800 --> 00:27:17,000
Before that,

412
00:27:17,960 --> 00:27:20,680
I want to show you something.

413
00:27:24,280 --> 00:27:26,360
Mo Lin left a letter to Ziyan.

414
00:27:27,640 --> 00:27:29,800
Yesterday’s incident happened suddenly.

415
00:27:29,800 --> 00:27:31,800
We haven’t had time to give it to you.

416
00:27:45,320 --> 00:27:45,880
Father.

417
00:27:47,640 --> 00:27:48,920
I am always lucky.

418
00:27:50,040 --> 00:27:51,120
But just in case,

419
00:27:51,520 --> 00:27:53,480
