420
00:27:54,240 --> 00:27:55,800
I must be dead.

421
00:27:56,880 --> 00:27:57,960
Don’t be too upset.

422
00:27:59,280 --> 00:28:00,610
Don’t be mad with Xifan.

423
00:28:02,240 --> 00:28:03,570
Shanhai Gang is fierce.

424
00:28:04,120 --> 00:28:06,580
He and Lu Ping have their responsibilities.

425
00:28:07,440 --> 00:28:09,840
I’m the most useless disciple in Zhaifeng.

426
00:28:10,080 --> 00:28:11,280
The only thing I can do

427
00:28:12,120 --> 00:28:13,720
is to try my best to help them.

428
00:28:15,680 --> 00:28:17,840
I want you to sincerely praise that

429
00:28:18,880 --> 00:28:20,560
I am indeed your son.

430
00:28:21,760 --> 00:28:24,320
I want my friends to sincerely praise that

431
00:28:25,840 --> 00:28:27,840
I am indeed their brother.

432
00:28:29,880 --> 00:28:30,720
This time,

433
00:28:32,320 --> 00:28:33,840
I would protect you.

434
00:28:34,720 --> 00:28:36,040
From your son, Mo Lin.

435
00:28:36,760 --> 00:28:38,040
Silly.

436
00:28:39,440 --> 00:28:41,240
He is silly.

437
00:28:43,040 --> 00:28:44,120
Mo Lin is not silly.

438
00:28:44,840 --> 00:28:46,880
He is the World’s No.1 Assassin

439
00:28:47,480 --> 00:28:49,340
and my most responsible brother.

440
00:28:51,680 --> 00:28:54,160
The chaos of Shanhai Gang endangers the world.

441
00:28:54,160 --> 00:28:56,080
Master Mo, please help and

442
00:28:56,400 --> 00:28:59,260
