443
00:29:06,440 --> 00:29:07,880
About the antidote,

444
00:29:08,760 --> 00:29:10,600
I will settle that.

445
00:29:11,520 --> 00:29:13,080
Not for you,

446
00:29:14,520 --> 00:29:15,880
but for my son.

447
00:29:17,320 --> 00:29:18,880
As a father,

448
00:29:19,400 --> 00:29:21,640
I want to finish this for my son.

449
00:29:25,680 --> 00:29:26,520
Well,

450
00:29:27,440 --> 00:29:30,880
you go and find some people who were imposed Xi Sui.

451
00:29:31,520 --> 00:29:34,440
Maybe I can find solutions

452
00:29:35,240 --> 00:29:37,400
among them.

453
00:29:39,920 --> 00:29:41,480
Thanks a lot, master.

454
00:29:42,600 --> 00:29:44,730
I have another presumptuous request.

455
00:29:45,120 --> 00:29:46,600
Can I meet Lu Ping?

456
00:29:47,560 --> 00:29:49,360
Lu Ping has gone.

457
00:29:50,880 --> 00:29:52,320
Did he say where he was going?

458
00:29:52,320 --> 00:29:53,920
Before Lu Ping went,

459
00:29:54,240 --> 00:29:56,000
he left a message for you.

460
00:29:56,920 --> 00:29:59,180
He said that your grudge had been paid off

461
00:29:59,840 --> 00:30:03,480
in the three moves of that day.

462
00:30:03,680 --> 00:30:06,960
Someone else needs to pay the rest.

463
00:30:07,840 --> 00:30:08,520
No.

464
00:30:09,400 --> 00:30:11,520
Lu Ping is going to seek revenge from His Majesty.

465
00:30:11,520 --> 00:30:12,120
News.

466
00:30:15,280 --> 00:30:15,740
Master.

467
00:30:15,880 --> 00:30:17,940
Miss Ling is in a hurry to send a letter

468
00:30:18,080 --> 00:30:19,360
to Mr. Xifan

469
00:30:33,680 --> 00:30:34,400
