493
00:31:52,640 --> 00:31:55,760
Yan Qiuci will be defeated.

494
00:32:02,160 --> 00:32:03,090
Eldest brother.

495
00:32:07,120 --> 00:32:08,600
It has been 19 years.

496
00:32:10,400 --> 00:32:14,600
You were so kind at that time.

497
00:32:15,800 --> 00:32:18,280
