516
00:34:19,400 --> 00:34:21,080
We don’t need to fight recklessly.

517
00:34:21,080 --> 00:34:23,480
Send these bodies to Wuyou Valley, please.

518
00:34:23,760 --> 00:34:25,889
Master Mo is working on the solutions.

519
00:34:26,150 --> 00:34:26,800
Yes.

520
00:34:27,670 --> 00:34:28,320
Xifan.

